{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-template-tsx","path":"/elixir/processes","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>very lightweight</li>\n<li>each process is isolated from each other</li>\n<li>a failure in a process will never crash or corrupt another process</li>\n<li>a process can be used to add state</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"spawn\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spawn\" aria-label=\"spawn permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>spawn</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>you can create a process using <code class=\"language-text\">spawn</code> function</li>\n<li>defined in <code class=\"language-text\">Kernel</code> module</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"elixir\"><pre class=\"language-elixir\"><code class=\"language-elixir\"><span class=\"token comment\"># run the function in another process</span>\npid <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> spawn <span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">end</span>\n\nProcess<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>alive?<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pid<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"send-and-receive\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#send-and-receive\" aria-label=\"send and receive permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>send and receive</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"elixir\"><pre class=\"language-elixir\"><code class=\"language-elixir\">iex<span class=\"token operator\">></span> send self<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token atom symbol\">:hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"world\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\niex<span class=\"token operator\">></span> receive <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token atom symbol\">:hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> msg<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> msg\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token atom symbol\">:word</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> _msg<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"no match\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">end</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"spawn_link\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spawn_link\" aria-label=\"spawn_link permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>spawn_link</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>allows process to establish relationship in case of failure</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 07, 2021","path":"/elixir/processes","title":"Processes","category":"Elixir"}}},"pageContext":{}}}